      "text": "Ele cria uma vaca. A vaca faz muu."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/ZXcbK3tIVw%2f1755808068101%2fKahala+18+Wahuwa+Anenama+a+Vaate%2fASP_170_Domestic_animals_Page_04_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Ele cria um cabrito. O cabrito faz méé."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/ZXcbK3tIVw%2f1755808068101%2fKahala+18+Wahuwa+Anenama+a+Vaate%2fASP_170_Domestic_animals_Page_05_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Ele cria um cavalo. O cavalo faz irráá."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/ZXcbK3tIVw%2f1755808068101%2fKahala+18+Wahuwa+Anenama+a+Vaate%2fASP_170_Domestic_animals_Page_06_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Ele cria um porco. O porco faz óinc, óinc."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/ZXcbK3tIVw%2f1755808068101%2fKahala+18+Wahuwa+Anenama+a+Vaate%2fASP_170_Domestic_animals_Page_07_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Ele cria uma galinha. A galinha faz cócóricó."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/ZXcbK3tIVw%2f1755808068101%2fKahala+18+Wahuwa+Anenama+a+Vaate%2fASP_170_Domestic_animals_Page_08_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Ele cria um cão. O cão faz au au."
    },
    {
